# The real identity-scrub checks live in sanitization/private/ — a folder you
# fill with your own private repo (see sanitization/README.md). It's ignored
# wholesale so those checks can never land in this public repo. The public
# README + example script sit at sanitization/ top level and ARE tracked, so a
# fresh clone still learns the system.
sanitization/private/

# Third-party Papyrus API stubs (MCM Helper, po3 Extender, SkyUI, PapyrusUtil,
# UIExtensions, and base-game signatures). Compile-time only, and not ours to
# redistribute - they belong to their authors - so they live here locally but stay
# out of the public repo. See docs/BUILDING.md for how to supply them.
headers/

# Local agent / review scratch
.scratch/

